_sText:
Eh, was planning on doing a bit more to this map. But due to time restraints and a lack of Temporal Over Abundance the 3d skybox will remain where it is; in my mind :/
fy_whoville_xmas Created by: Semp part of the FPSBANANA '08 Christmas contest Info: And he puzzled three hours, `till his puzzler was sore. Then the Grinch thought of something he hadn’t before! “Maybe Christmas,” he thought, “doesn’t come from a store. “Maybe Christmas, perhaps, means a little bit more!” Hopfully this map will make your christmas less of a bore! BSP Contains: - LDR and HDR lighting - Custom models - Custom textures - Overview/Radar - Cubemaps (both LDR and HDR) - Credit (.txt) file - Custom soundscape (mix of default Valve sounds)
Also, the zipped folder contains a full .nav file (for AI/bots) Credits: Semp (duh) mr. kit (for the custom models, we all <3 you) G-FLOW (custom skybox "flowsky11") FPSBanana (http://www.fpsbanana.com) Compiled for Counter Strike: Source (GG-mod compatible).
